package DAO
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AppointmentAccess
    The AppointmentAccess class provides methods to access and manage appointment data in the database.
    ContactAccess
    This class represents the data access object (DAO) responsible for retrieving and handling contact-related data from a database using JDBC.
    CountryAccess
    The CountryAccess class provides methods to access and manage country information in the database.
    CustomerAccess
    The CustomerAccess class provides methods to access and manage customer information in the database.

    The FirstLevelDivisionAccess class provides methods to access and manage first-level division information in the database.
    ReportAccess
    The ReportAccess class provides methods to access and generate reports related to appointments and countries.

    The UserAccess class provides methods to access and manipulate user-related data from the database.
